public class BootDao
extends org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.support.HibernateDaoSupport

The Data access class for boats. All Interaction with the database regarding the entity bean Boot should be handled by this class!

findFreie

public java.util.List<Boot> findFreie()
Returns the list of Boot objects which are currently not on a trip. The method works as follows:
  • An HQL query is specified and stored in a string variable
  • Retrieve all Boot objects from the db
  • Create an empty list for results and empty boats

Returns:
a List of Boot
